<s docid="FT931-2858" num="7" wdcount="12"> The market reopened on Monday in an 
attempt to return to normal.</s>
<s docid="FT931-2858" num="8" wdcount="30"> It has had to compromise - trading has 
been restricted to an hour a day, and dealing has moved back to the traditional 
